===Etymology===
* ''c.'' '''701-762:''' [[w:Li Bai|Li Bai]], ''Gazing at the Mount Lu waterfalls part two of two'' (望廬山瀑布水詩二首之二)
*: [[飛]][[流]][[直]][[下]][[三]][[千]][[尺]]，[[疑]][[是]]'''銀河落九天'''。
*:: ''The torrent flew through the air and dropped 3,000 meters straight down, it seemed as if '''the Milky way was falling into the Ninth Heaven'''''
